    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/d160cfe79552f1b8f1aa71b25fd56013.avif?t=1725487910\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/c8bc474b0b0d897f174b964f8b1ca0b6.poster.avif?t=1725487910\" width=600 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/c8bc474b0b0d897f174b964f8b1ca0b6.webm?t=1725487910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/c8bc474b0b0d897f174b964f8b1ca0b6.mp4?t=1725487910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>St. Dinfina Hotel位于Treze Trilhas，是一家衰落的酒店，它大量传闻都脱不了干系，其中就包括神秘失踪和超自然现象。为了做追踪报道，业余记者罗伯托·莱特·洛佩斯按照好友斯蒂芬妮的提示前往圣卡塔琳娜。<br><br>主角发现了一部照相机，并通过它了解到存在不同时间线、一个狂热的异教组织、人体实验和游荡于酒店大厅的幽灵，此时，身为记者所具备的调查技能不仅可以帮助他揭开事件背后的真相，而且当现实世界被搅得天翻地覆时更能救他一命。玩家在游戏中跨越过去，现在和未来的不同时间线解开各种谜题，并想尽一切办法阻止异教徒们的猎杀。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/b51e86bd7580d74a4e571805bd2125b4.poster.avif?t=1725487910\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/b51e86bd7580d74a4e571805bd2125b4.webm?t=1725487910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/b51e86bd7580d74a4e571805bd2125b4.mp4?t=1725487910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/413c5fbfb64051e57084e7403af8fa05.avif?t=1725487910\" width=600 height=80 /></span><br>•探索一间豪华酒店 – 这款第一人称生存恐怖游戏采用虚幻引擎，可以为玩家带来惊悚逼真的视角效果。<br>•生存恐怖 – 一边逃命、躲避或与游荡于酒店走廊的怪物战斗，一边搜集各种物资。<br>•解开谜团 – 现实世界和平行世界激烈碰撞，剧情跌宕起伏，大量谜题和阴谋充斥其中。<br>•回顾过去，放眼未来 – 利用连接平行空间的神秘照相机跨越不同时间线，揭开隐藏在酒店高墙后的众多秘密。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/33ca8507a0287e5d09c1ec63cce60c07.poster.avif?t=1725487910\" width=600 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/33ca8507a0287e5d09c1ec63cce60c07.webm?t=1725487910\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1298140/extras/33ca8507a0287e5d09c1ec63cce60c07.mp4?t=1725487910\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
